paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information for BRCA2, including penetrance data.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: Using NextGENe analysis, we discovered one false-positive call (BRCA2 NM_000059.3: c.8953+15_8953+16insT) in a patient.

functional_data.summary: The error was confirmed as a strand bias with low balance ratio of 0.169.

variants.additional_notes: This variant was identified as a false positive.
